Doug Farmer
05/11/2001 06:09 PM

To: Peter E Weidler/ENRON_DEVELOPMENT@ENRON_DEVELOPMENT, 
Hansvander.klink@shell.com.br, Hans.h.vanderklink@si.shell.com
cc: Jan van den Berg/TRANSREDES@TRANSREDES, John 
